{"title": "Balancing the potential of Singtel\u2019s ambitious 3-year strategy with \u2018hidden\u2019 risks", "tags": "business", "timestamp": "2024-06-27", "content": "SINGAPORE \u2013 When Singtel released its full-year results in late May, it also unveiled its next strategic plan \u2013 dubbed Singtel28 (ST28) \u2013 that focuses on \u201csustained value realisation\u201d.\nSo far, analysts have been overwhelmingly positive about the three-year plan. Some 12 out of the 13 recommendations on Bloomberg are advocating \u201cbuy\u201d or \u201cadd\u201d."}